OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fevening sunshine away from the coast,
OL,7,Fany showers will ease into the
OL,8,Fevening. Overnight the patchy low
OL,9,Fcloud may spread inland, with some
OL,10,Fhill fog possible.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FAn outbreak of showers is
OL,13,Fpossible early in the morning, with
OL,14,Fany low cloud or hill fog quickly
OL,15,Fclearing away. Then another dry day
OL,16,Fwith sunny intervals.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
